Virtual "Disbursement of funds received under District Annual Plan (General Plan)"

A request has been made to declare a "Virtual Personal Deposit Account Administrator." Accordingly, the issue of declaring a "Virtual Personal Deposit Account Administrator" for these institutions / colleges / Administrative Pre-Service Training Centres was under consideration of the Government.

Government Decisions: - Government Decisions, Department of Finance, Govt. As per the provisions of the 14.02.2024, the District Planning Committee for the 34 functioning Lower Schedule Institutions / Colleges / Administrative Pre-Service Training Centres under the Directorate of Higher Education has constituted the District Planning Committee (DAC) under the District Annual Plan (General Plan) to allocate the funds received from the District Level Plan for "Development of Government Colleges." and a) has been approved by the Office subject to the conditions mentioned in the Annexure accompanying this Government Decision. Accordingly, it is being approved to declare Virtual Personal Deposit Account Administrator for the schemes implemented by the Directorate of Higher Education as follows:
